  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791290/extras/b96aa85a548709276e90196aacae6d3e.poster.avif?t=1750528398\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791290/extras/b96aa85a548709276e90196aacae6d3e.webm?t=1750528398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791290/extras/b96aa85a548709276e90196aacae6d3e.mp4?t=1750528398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>REVOLUTIONIZE YOUR AIM TRAINING</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Step into Aim Zen, where traditional aim training evolves into an immersive journey of skill mastery. Unlike conventional trainers, Aim Zen introduces a groundbreaking Musical Heaven mode that synchronizes training with rhythm, making every session both productive and enjoyable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791290/extras/f2db2cf8673b18651613c9aa63544d10.poster.avif?t=1750528398\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791290/extras/f2db2cf8673b18651613c9aa63544d10.webm?t=1750528398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791290/extras/f2db2cf8673b18651613c9aa63544d10.mp4?t=1750528398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MUSICAL HEAVEN: WHERE RHYTHM MEETS PRECISION</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Experience aim training like never before with the signature Musical Heaven mode. Feel the flow as shots sync with the beat across 20+ carefully curated tracks. This isn't just practice – it's a performance where every successful shot creates a symphony of satisfaction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791290/extras/1eba10d6f3b433de9dc41571de9fee8a.poster.avif?t=1750528398\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791290/extras/1eba10d6f3b433de9dc41571de9fee8a.webm?t=1750528398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791290/extras/1eba10d6f3b433de9dc41571de9fee8a.mp4?t=1750528398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COMPREHENSIVE TRAINING ARSENAL</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Master every aspect of aim through specialized training modes. From Gridshot's precision flicking to Reflex mode's reaction training, each mode is crafted to enhance specific aspects of gameplay. Perfect headshots, develop smooth tracking, and master accuracy while in motion - all within one comprehensive package.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791290/extras/ba7d71a5511bb7ee5e84f0a9fbf465cc.poster.avif?t=1750528398\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791290/extras/ba7d71a5511bb7ee5e84f0a9fbf465cc.webm?t=1750528398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791290/extras/ba7d71a5511bb7ee5e84f0a9fbf465cc.mp4?t=1750528398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COMPLETE TRAINING SUITE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Aim Zen provides everything needed for effective practice. The Zen Editor enables creating and customizing training scenarios to match specific needs. Track progress with session statistics and performance analytics, while the progression system helps maintain motivation. Built with performance in mind, Aim Zen runs smoothly on most systems with FSR support and various graphics settings for optimal performance. Whether creating custom scenarios, analyzing improvement, or fine-tuning settings, all tools needed to enhance skills are readily available.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791290/extras/d75fd2fc94e626165dd28ee67192f510.poster.avif?t=1750528398\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791290/extras/d75fd2fc94e626165dd28ee67192f510.webm?t=1750528398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791290/extras/d75fd2fc94e626165dd28ee67192f510.mp4?t=1750528398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start your journey to aim mastery today with Aim Zen.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791290/extras/b96aa85a548709276e90196aacae6d3e.poster.avif?t=1750528398\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791290/extras/b96aa85a548709276e90196aacae6d3e.webm?t=1750528398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791290/extras/b96aa85a548709276e90196aacae6d3e.mp4?t=1750528398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>REVOLUTIONIZE YOUR AIM TRAINING</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Step into Aim Zen, where traditional aim training evolves into an immersive journey of skill mastery. Unlike conventional trainers, Aim Zen introduces a groundbreaking Musical Heaven mode that synchronizes training with rhythm, making every session both productive and enjoyable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791290/extras/f2db2cf8673b18651613c9aa63544d10.poster.avif?t=1750528398\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791290/extras/f2db2cf8673b18651613c9aa63544d10.webm?t=1750528398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791290/extras/f2db2cf8673b18651613c9aa63544d10.mp4?t=1750528398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MUSICAL HEAVEN: WHERE RHYTHM MEETS PRECISION</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Experience aim training like never before with the signature Musical Heaven mode. Feel the flow as shots sync with the beat across 20+ carefully curated tracks. This isn't just 